### 2. Disk Space Troubleshooting & LVM Expansion

**Issue:** Dashboard installation failed with `No space left on device`.

**Commands Used to Diagnose:**

```bash
df -h
lsblk
sudo pvs
sudo vgs
sudo lvs
```

**LVM Expansion Command:**

```bash
sudo lvextend --resizefs -l +100%FREE /dev/ubuntu-vg/ubuntu-lv
```

**Alternative LVM Expansion Command:**

```bash
sudo lvextend -l +100%FREE -r /dev/mapper/ubuntu--vg-ubuntu--lv
```

**Verification:**

```bash
df -h /
```

**Result:**

```text
/dev/mapper/ubuntu--vg-ubuntu--lv   47G   12G   33G  26% /
```

