### 4. macOS Agent Deployment

**Download macOS Agent Package:**

```bash
curl -sO https://packages.wazuh.com/4.x/macos/wazuh-agent-4.7.0-1.pkg
```

**Set Wazuh Manager IP and Install:**

```bash
sudo launchctl setenv WAZUH_MANAGER "192.168.190.138" && sudo installer -pkg wazuh-agent-4.7.0-1.pkg -target /
```

**Alternative Installation Method:**

```bash
echo "WAZUH_MANAGER='192.168.190.138'" > /tmp/wazuh_envs && sudo installer -pkg wazuh-agent-4.7.0-1.pkg -target /
```

**Start the Wazuh Agent on macOS:**

```bash
sudo /Library/Ossec/bin/wazuh-control start
```

**Check Agent Status on macOS:**

```bash
sudo launchctl list | grep wazuh-agent
```

**Verify Agent Communication:**

```bash
sudo /Library/Ossec/bin/agent_control -lc
```

**Dashboard Verification:**

```text
Agent: Lafleur.local
Status: Active
```

