### 5. File Integrity Monitoring (FIM) Configuration

**Configuration File Path (macOS):**

```text
/Library/Ossec/etc/ossec.conf
```

**Working `syscheck` Block:**

```xml
<syscheck>
  <disabled>no</disabled>
  <frequency>60</frequency>
  <scan_on_start>yes</scan_on_start>
  <alert_new_files>yes</alert_new_files>
  <directories check_all="yes" report_changes="yes">/Users/lafleur/wazuh-fim-test</directories>
  <skip_nfs>yes</skip_nfs>
  <skip_dev>yes</skip_dev>
  <skip_proc>yes</skip_proc>
  <skip_sys>yes</skip_sys>
</syscheck>
```

**Restart Agent After Configuration Change:**

```bash
sudo /Library/Ossec/bin/wazuh-control restart
```

